Introduction

Cosmic Girls αγυρτης (The Imposter) is a captivating sub-unit within the renowned female group WJSN. Comprising members Xuan Yi, EXY, Soobin, Eunseo, and Cheng Xiao, this enigmatic ensemble brings a unique blend of talents to the stage. Notably, Eunseo joined the unit on September 9, 2018.

Their thematic essence revolves around being “collectors of floating dreams.” As second-year students at the illustrious WJSN School of Magic, they specialize in gathering people’s dreams—an intriguing and otherworldly pursuit. Described as balanced, strange, mysterious, and intelligent, Cosmic Girls αγυρτης adds an ethereal dimension to WJSN’s musical universe.
